N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 94.5 - Supplier defined

State Regulations

For purposes of subdivisions (b) and (d) of section
94.3, subdivisions (a), (b) and (c)
of section
94.4, and section
94.6
of this Part, an out-of-State
or foreign brewer and its brand agent in this State shall be deemed to be a
single "supplier."
